lass=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ujait.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jait</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/21/02 10:46:39 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1440.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: address</span><hr size=1> Taunt is known.  Its been known for over 2 years from the old whineplay boards.<br><br><br>It's very simple. <br><br>1) Taunt does not always work. <br><br>2) When it does work it moves you exactly 1 point higher on the hatelist then the #1. <br><br>3) However in mass damage fights with DoTs and other spells on the mob you might not see that take place even on a successful taunt but it does happen.  It just happens fast.  Just because you dont *see* it doesent mean it isnt happening.<br><br>Also keep in mind that since the release of RoK much of this changed for post 50 mobs.  You can only taunt your level and lower and some mobs are flagged untauntable. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ufuloriancavestomper.showPublicProfile?language=EN>FulorianCavestomper</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>/con's RED</span><br>  Posts: 391<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/21/02 10:55:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1440.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: address</span><hr size=1> Your giving the generic speech that all the brainless people who think this is a 'proven fact' give. Taunt does NOT work that way, even on mobs that are 'Tauntable'. I've long been an advocate that its a hate increaser, based off what you've already DONE, and nothing else. <p><img src